result.title: World Finals Regional Champions
result.content:
Besides guessing the medals, I think it's also interesting to guess the regional champions.

Latin American Champion: Universidad Nacional de CÃ³rdoba

And I'm also guessing that I wrote them according to their relative order in the scoreboard.
